fromPort.description: The first port, inclusive, in the range of ports for the endpoint group that is associated with a custom routing accelerator.

protocols.description: The protocol for the endpoint group that is associated with a custom routing accelerator. The protocol can be either `"TCP"` or `"UDP"`.

toPort.description: The last port, inclusive, in the range of ports for the endpoint group that is associated with a custom routing accelerator.
